===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|gerundium|lang=la}}, from {{term|gerundus||which is to be carried out|lang=la}}, future passive participle ([[gerundive]]) of {{term|gerō||carry, bear|lang=la}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|jěr'-ənd}}, {{IPA|/ˈdʒɛrənd/|/-ʌnd/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|ɛrənd|ɛrʌnd|lang=en}}

